entries.abort: Ha, I knew you would run from the great NEZZO!
entries.arrival_phase_1: Stand by for location of Nezzo Milli's ship.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Ship located. Nezzo is considered dangerous. Proceed with caution.
entries.capture_complete: Autopilot has been reprogrammed. Escort vessel back to safe jump point.
entries.capture_phase_1: Hey, you can't do that! Don't you know who I am?
entries.capture_phase_2: So you think you have heard the last of NEZZO? I will show you...one day I shall have my revenge.
entries.capture_started: Beginning autopilot reprogramming sequence. Stand by.
entries.complete: We have Nezzo back with us. We will be sure to see that he gets the help he needs.
entries.failed_destroy: We wanted him back in one piece, not dead. That ship was valuable property.
entries.failed_escape: You let that lunatic get away! What kind of fighter pilot are you?
entries.recovery_success: The vessel is now jumping out of the system. Stand by.
entries.split_quest_alert: Your next assignment is to travel to Endor and help our shipping fleet against a band of environmental radicals known as the Greenburst.
entries.target_disabled: His ship is offline. Move in close while we trigger the flight computer overrride.
entries.title: Space Lok: Capture Nezzo Milli
